column2: select AssetID=a.ID, AssetNodeDist=an.NodeDist, TractID=t.ID, TractNodeDist=tn.NodeDist, d.* from optw.tamass.ASSETS a    left join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Assets an on a.ID=an.ID    left join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Drive d on an.NodeID=d.OrigNodeID or an.NodeID=d.DestNodeID   left join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Tracts tn on tn.NodeID=d.OrigNodeID or tn.NodeID=d.DestNodeID   left join optw.tamass.TRACTS t on tn.ID=t.ID where an.NodeDist < @nodedistmax and tn.NodeDist < @nodedistmax    and Minutes > # order by AssetID, TractID
